


@@BEGIN: WORKSHOP
@id: workshop2
@title: Metadata with Google Sheets
@date: 2024-10-23
@time: 16:30
@presenter: Benjamin Ory, Craig Stuart Sapp, Jacek Iwaszko
@slides: https://bit.ly/IDCM-metadata
@abstract: 

	This workshop offers a foundational introduction to organising
	and displaying metadata on the web using <a target="_blank"
	href="https://workspace.google.com/products/sheets">Google
	Sheets</a>.  This user-friendly approach to data management
	enables individuals without significant technical expertise to
	create and collaboratively editable metadata for web-based
	applications. We will explore various projects that employ this
	methodand demonstrate how to export metadata with <a target="_blank"
	href="https://developers.google.com/apps-script/overview">Google
	Apps Scripts</a> to convert worksheets into JSON data.  The
	JSON data can then be used to dynamically update a webpage
	or downloaded for static integration.

@@END: WORKSHOP



